    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Cut your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable</strong> <strong>stock</strong> <strong>mix</strong> and <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>paste</strong> in 500ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[650ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1L] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p>",
