        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>parsley</strong>, <strong>saffron</strong> and a squeeze of <strong>lemon juice </strong>in a bowl with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive</strong> <strong>oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your <strong>saffron & lemon dressing</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon </strong>into 1 wedge per person</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1706622104790-x200.jpg",
