    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic </strong>with your <strong>ground smoked</strong> <strong>paprika</strong> and <strong>dried thyme</strong> and cook for<strong> </strong>1<strong> </strong>min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>orzo</strong> and stir to coat the grains in the spices</p>",
      "order": 5,
