    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once cooked, stir through your <strong>blanched peas</strong> with a grind of<strong> black pepper </strong>and cook<strong> </strong>for a further 1 min or until warmed through – this is your <strong>Spanish-style orzo</strong></p>",
